author: Kristina Wong
title: Reps. Jim Banks, Seth Moulton Introduce Bipartisan Bill Condemning China
description: Reps. Jim Banks and Seth Moulton introduced a bipartisan bill condemning the Chinese government for its handling of the coronavirus outbreak.
content:
Reps. Jim Banks (R-IN) and Seth Moulton (D-MA) introduced a bill condemning the Chinese government for its handling of the coronavirus outbreak, in a sign of bipartisan anger against China.
